[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 6946,
        "end_time": 11001,
        "text": "Honeybees are fascinating creatures \nfor a number of reasons:"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 11001,
        "end_time": 12382,
        "text": "their incredible work ethic,"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 12382,
        "end_time": 14320,
        "text": "the sugary sweet syrup they produce"
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 14320,
        "end_time": 16468,
        "text": "and their intricate social structure."
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 16468,
        "end_time": 19754,
        "text": "But another reason is \nthat honeybees are, in fact,"
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 19754,
        "end_time": 21767,
        "text": "excellent mathematicians."
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 21767,
        "end_time": 25292,
        "text": "Scientists claim the tiny insects \ncan calculate angles,"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 25292,
        "end_time": 28692,
        "text": "and can even comprehend\nthe roundness of the Earth."
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 28692,
        "end_time": 31252,
        "text": "But there&#39;s particular\nmathematical bee genius"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 31252,
        "end_time": 34961,
        "text": "behind the most important aspect \nof honeybee life: the hive."
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 34961,
        "end_time": 38954,
        "text": "Just like humans, bees need food\nand shelter to stay alive."
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 38954,
        "end_time": 41032,
        "text": "The hive is not only the bees&#39; home,"
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 41032,
        "end_time": 43731,
        "text": "but doubles as a place\nto store their honey."
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 43731,
        "end_time": 46433,
        "text": "Since it&#39;s so central to survival,"
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 46433,
        "end_time": 49793,
        "text": "honeybees have to perfect\nthe hive&#39;s architectural design."
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 49793,
        "end_time": 52616,
        "text": "If you examine any piece of honeycomb,"
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 52616,
        "end_time": 54092,
        "text": "you&#39;ll see that it&#39;s constructed from"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 54092,
        "end_time": 58175,
        "text": "tightly packed hexagonal, \nor six-sided, cells."
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 58175,
        "end_time": 59686,
        "text": "Of all the possible designs,"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 59686,
        "end_time": 62038,
        "text": "why do honeybees choose this one?"
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 62038,
        "end_time": 64817,
        "text": "To understand, you need\nto think like a bee."
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 64817,
        "end_time": 68372,
        "text": "Bees need a secure place \nfor their entire colony to live."
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 68372,
        "end_time": 70227,
        "text": "Similarly, there needs to be a place"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 70227,
        "end_time": 73085,
        "text": "where their nectar can \nbe stored and ripened suitably"
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 73085,
        "end_time": 74585,
        "text": "until it turns into honey."
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 74595,
        "end_time": 78519,
        "text": "That means there&#39;s a need\nfor some serious space efficiency."
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 78519,
        "end_time": 82060,
        "text": "A good solution is to build\nlittle storage units, or cells,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 82060,
        "end_time": 84680,
        "text": "just big enough for a bee to fit into,"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 84680,
        "end_time": 88361,
        "text": "which can also double as the containers\nin which nectar is stored:"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 88361,
        "end_time": 90650,
        "text": "The bees&#39; very own honey jars."
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 90650,
        "end_time": 94558,
        "text": "The next thing, is to decide what\nthe little cells should be made out of."
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 94558,
        "end_time": 97484,
        "text": "Bees don&#39;t have beaks\nor arms to pick up things,"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 97484,
        "end_time": 100030,
        "text": "but they are capable of producing wax."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 100030,
        "end_time": 103412,
        "text": "The thing is, producing it \nis a lot of hard work."
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 103412,
        "end_time": 105939,
        "text": "Bees have to consume 8 ounces of honey"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 105939,
        "end_time": 108618,
        "text": "to produce just 1 ounce of wax."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 108618,
        "end_time": 110386,
        "text": "So they don&#39;t want to waste it."
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 110386,
        "end_time": 113032,
        "text": "So, they need a design \nthat allows them to store"
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 113032,
        "end_time": 115302,
        "text": "the largest possible amount of honey"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 115302,
        "end_time": 117578,
        "text": "using the least amount of wax."
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 117578,
        "end_time": 119065,
        "text": "What shape does that?"
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 119065,
        "end_time": 121133,
        "text": "Imagining for a minute \nthat all bees had to"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 121133,
        "end_time": 124153,
        "text": "attend architecture academy \nand go to math class."
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 124153,
        "end_time": 126681,
        "text": "Let&#39;s say they asked \ntheir geometry teacher,"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 126681,
        "end_time": 130011,
        "text": "&quot;What shape would give us\nthe most space to store our honey,"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 130011,
        "end_time": 132418,
        "text": "but require the least amount of wax?&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 132418,
        "end_time": 134007,
        "text": "And then geometry teacher replied,"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 134007,
        "end_time": 136686,
        "text": "&quot;The shape that you&#39;re seeking \nis the circle.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 136686,
        "end_time": 139362,
        "text": "Leaving the bees to return\nto their trial construction site"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 139362,
        "end_time": 143047,
        "text": "and begin building their honeycomb\nusing circular cells."
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 143047,
        "end_time": 145590,
        "text": "After a while, some of them \nmight have noticed"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 145590,
        "end_time": 147259,
        "text": "a problem with their design:"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 147259,
        "end_time": 149837,
        "text": "small gaps between the cells."
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 149837,
        "end_time": 152508,
        "text": "&quot;We can&#39;t even fit in there! \nThat&#39;s wasted space!&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 152508,
        "end_time": 154103,
        "text": "they might have thought."
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 154103,
        "end_time": 155952,
        "text": "So, ignoring the geometry lesson,"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 155952,
        "end_time": 158229,
        "text": "and taking matters into their own hands,"
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 158229,
        "end_time": 159921,
        "text": "the bees went back to the drawing board"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 159921,
        "end_time": 162147,
        "text": "to rethink their beehive design."
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 162147,
        "end_time": 163719,
        "text": "One suggested triangles,"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 163719,
        "end_time": 167319,
        "text": "&quot;We can use triangles. Look! \nThey fit together perfectly.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 167319,
        "end_time": 169950,
        "text": "Another bee suggested squares."
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 169950,
        "end_time": 172035,
        "text": "Finally, a third bee piped up and said,"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 172035,
        "end_time": 175305,
        "text": "&quot;Pentagons don&#39;t seem to work, \nbut hexagons do!"
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 175305,
        "end_time": 178081,
        "text": "We want the one that will use \nthe least amount of wax"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 178081,
        "end_time": 180553,
        "text": "and be able to store \nthe most amount of honey."
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 180553,
        "end_time": 182990,
        "text": "Yes, I think that&#39;s the hexagon.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 182990,
        "end_time": 184175,
        "text": "&quot;Why?&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 184175,
        "end_time": 186281,
        "text": "&quot;It looks more like the circle \nthan the others.&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 186281,
        "end_time": 188072,
        "text": "&quot;But how do we know for sure?&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 188072,
        "end_time": 190902,
        "text": "To find out, the industrious \ninsect architects"
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 190902,
        "end_time": 194804,
        "text": "calculated the areas of the triangle,\nthe square and the hexagon"
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 194804,
        "end_time": 197002,
        "text": "and found that the hexagon was, in fact,"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 197002,
        "end_time": 200251,
        "text": "the shape that gave them\nthe most storage space."
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 200251,
        "end_time": 203389,
        "text": "They agreed on an ideal size \nand returned to work."
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 203389,
        "end_time": 206229,
        "text": "The space efficient comb that \nis a bee&#39;s trademark today,"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 206229,
        "end_time": 208670,
        "text": "is probably the result \nof this trial and error,"
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 208670,
        "end_time": 211611,
        "text": "but over long periods \nof evolutionary history."
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 211611,
        "end_time": 213363,
        "text": "However, it paid off."
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 213363,
        "end_time": 214664,
        "text": "Peek into any hive --"
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 214664,
        "end_time": 217063,
        "text": "with your protective goggles \nand netting on, of course --"
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 217063,
        "end_time": 220826,
        "text": "and you&#39;ll see the end result: \na beautiful compact honeycomb"
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 220826,
        "end_time": 223812,
        "text": "that any architect would have \nbe proud to design."
    }
]